Instalar programas (Ubuntu/Debian)
sudo apt update
sudo apt install nginx
sudo apt remove nginx

Atualizar sistema
sudo apt upgrade

Serviços (systemd)
systemctl status nginx
systemctl start nginx
systemctl stop nginx
systemctl restart nginx
systemctl enable nginx

Uso do sistema
top   (sair q)
htop
df -h     # disco
free -h   # memória
